{"tid":1603770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去到今時今日 我覺得香港獨立已經唔係無可能既事","createTime":"2019-09-29T18:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T19:00:41.000Z","uid":48873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a33d4eaf1508803d033aa62636471e61fa5418fa","tid":1603770,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:18:42.000Z","msg":"國旗有 黑色洋紫荊<br />\n國歌有 Glory to Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n國際地位 基建 自己既語言文化，都有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟本香港同中國兩回事黎，融合咗22年啦 融到咩？<br />\n大家想保留香港 自治真係一條路黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有感而發。<br />\n十月一號 賀佢老母 全民黑色攝衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80418d29796011aaf5becc6aed660754b0043b2a","tid":1603770,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">若特區政府無法履行其憲制責任落實真正的雙普選，我等將另闢新徑，設法重新建立尊重民意的議會、政府及憲制。<br />\n<br />\nWe are ready to rise up when necessary by forming a provisional parliament, drafting a new constitution, and establishing a provisional government.</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhwF7kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhwF7kd.jpg&h=5781479b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v40Ly0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv40Ly0d.jpg&h=3864b67f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原po在此：<br />\n【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a></span>"},{"pid":"2cd07a5ab0d4e4c0cf3db0a0644e175483468f4e","tid":1603770,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"全球反共要繼續進行 唔可以停"},{"pid":"fc38b071ec66f71f95b962bd5b38230b3e642cd2","tid":1603770,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd07a5ab0d4e4c0cf3db0a0644e175483468f4e","tid":1603770,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"全球反共要繼續進行 唔可以停"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2399200203661388?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1474101479504603%2Fposts%2F2399200203661388%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=b856ddb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2399200203661388?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為大家介紹，一位日本人singer songwriter珠夢改編並cover了願榮光歸香港，這個版本甚有八十年代中島美雪feel，別有一番味道。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_CfG0d4K34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3_CfG0d4K34&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=8b490a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_CfG0d4K34</a><br />\n<br />\n珠夢official website<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shuyu.website/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuyu.website%2F&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=2a459009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shuyu.website/</a><br />\n<br />\n自由を求める香港市民が、街頭で歌っている「願榮光歸香港 (Glory to Hong Kong)」。その想いが日本人にも届くよう、珠夢の訳詩・編曲・歌で日本語版にしました。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後好感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164dcd1c519061aec02c292d627c08a685506452","tid":1603770,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:52:23.000Z","msg":"國旗有 黑色洋紫荊<br />\n國歌有 Glory to Hong Kong<br />\n國際地位 基建 自己既語言文化，都有<br />\n<br />\n咁就有條件有能力攪獨立?  中共會放過你?"},{"pid":"8d76f8bd729e3902345554346dbd3acfbfd19568","tid":1603770,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"差在香港人嘅決心"}]}